        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownDawnstarFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionDawnstar\")",
        "content": "Windward Ruins is a small set of broken Imperial stones north of Dawnstar — bandits use the place as a forward camp when the watch isn't looking.",
        "display_name": "Windward Ruins",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.55,
