        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownDawnstarFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionDawnstar\")",
        "content": "Silverdrift Lair is the Nordic ruin in the Pale's southern mountains — draugr hold the chambers, and the dead bandits littering the floor suggest the treasure wasn't taken without cost.",
        "display_name": "Silverdrift Lair",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.7,
