        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownDawnstarFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionDawnstar\")",
        "content": "Duskglow Crevice is a cave south of Dawnstar where Falmer have built a camp in the deep chambers — the few bandits still inside are losing their war with the blind cave-dwellers.",
        "display_name": "Duskglow Crevice",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.65,
