        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownDawnstarFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionDawnstar\")",
        "content": "Weynon Stones is a small standing-stone circle in the Pale — older than the Empire, older than the holds. People still leave offerings out of habit.",
